          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "- By Authors: the Half-Life has Been Measured by the",
                "Authors with Accuracy +/- 0.1 Hour.",
                "-By Authors: Briefly,Gallium and Zinc Carriers were",
                "Added and Gallium was Separated from Zinc and Most",
                "Fission Products by Twice Extracting.The Time of the",
                "Second Ether Extraction was Used As the Time of",
                "Separation of Ga-72 from Zn-72.Gallium was Further",
                "Purified by a Number of Scavenging Precipitations and",
                "Repeated Extractions.The Two Samples Obtained,Ga-1 and",
                "Ga-2 were Made to Equal Volume in Counting Vials and",
                "The Activity Determined.Since All Measurements were",
                "Relative,Absolute Disintegration Rates did not have to",
                "Be Determined.",
                "Ga-1 Showed a Very High Proportion of the 4.87-Hour",
                "Ga-73.When this was Allowed to Decay,the 14.1-Hour",
                "Ga-72 Could be Quate Easily Measured,Although at the",
                "Very Lowest Bombardment Energies the Activity of Ga-72",
                "Was Very Low.The Ga-2 Samples Generally Showed a Pure",
                " 14.1-Hour Decay Curve."
              ]
            }
          ],
